              "free_text": [
                "",
                " Thermal neutron absorption cross section"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " SIGt at Maxwellian spectrum of 380 K was derived from",
                "formulas :",
                " SIGlattice = SIGt + 0.055*I,",
                " SIGwell = SIGt + 0.010*I,",
                "where I - resonance absorption integral with 0.2 cutoff",
                "energy,",
                "coefficients 0.010 and 0.055 were determined in",
                "additional measuremnt by In foils with and without Cd",
                " ( 0.25mm, cut of 0.4 eV, counting 30-60 min ), taking",
                " 0.2 eV as point of transition between the Maxwellian",
                " spectrum and dE/E spectrum."
              ]
            }
          ],
